div>\n\n{{ bare_fiber_services|json_script:"cutover-bare-fiber-services" }}\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n    \'use strict\';\n    \n    // 初始化选点定位功能\n    function initMapPicker() {\n        const longitudeInput = document.getElementById(\'id_cutover_longitude\');\n        if (!longitudeInput) return;\n        \n        // 动态注入图标按钮到经度输入框右侧\n        const inputGroup = longitudeInput.closest(\'.input-group\');\n        let btnOpenMap;\n        \n        if (inputGroup) {\n            btnOpenMap = document.createElement(\'button\');\n            btnOpenMap.type = \'button\';\n            btnOpenMap.className = \'btn btn-outline-secondary\';\n            btnOpenMap.id = \'btn-open-map-picker\';\n            btnOpenMap.title = \'在地图上选点定位\';\n            btnOpenMap.innerHTML = \'<i class="mdi mdi-map-marker-radius"></i>\';\n            btnOpenMap.style.cssText = \'padding: 0.375rem 0.5rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.1rem;\';\n            inputGroup.appendChild(btnOpenMap);\n        } else {\n            const wrapper = document.createElement(\'div\');\n            wrapper.className = \'input-group\';\n            longitudeInput.parentNode.insertBefore(wrapper, longitudeInput);\n            wrapper.appendChild(longitudeInput);\n            \n            btnOpenMap = document.createElement(\'button\');\n            btnOpenMap.type = \'button\';\n            btnOpenMap.className = \'btn btn-outline-secondary\';\n            btnOpenMap.id = \'btn-open-map-picker\';\n            btnOpenMap.title = \'在地图上选点定位\';\n            btnOpenMap.innerHTML = \'<i class="mdi mdi-map-marker-radius"></i>\';\n            btnOpenMap.style.cssText = \'padding: 0.375rem 0.5rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.1rem;\';\n            wrapper.appendChild(btnOpenMap);\n        }\n        \n        // 创建模态窗口 (纯 DOM 控制，不依赖 bootstrap.Modal API)\n        const modalHtml = `\n        <div class="modal fade" id="mapPickerModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="mapPickerModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">\n            <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-centered">\n                <div class="modal-content">\n                    <div class="modal-header py-2">\n                        <h5 class="modal-title" id="mapPickerModalLabel">\n                            <i class="mdi mdi-map-marker-radius me-1"></i>地图选点定位\n                        </h5>\n                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" id="mapPickerCloseBtn" aria-label="Close"></button>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class="modal-body p-0">\n                        <iframe id="mapPickerIframe" style="width: 100%; height: 70vh; border: none;"></iframe>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>`;\n        document.body.insertAdjacentHTML(\'beforeend\', modalHtml);\n        \n        const modalEl = document.getElementById(\'mapPickerModal\');\n        const iframe = document.getElementById(\'mapPickerIframe\');\n        const closeBtn = document.getElementById(\'mapPickerCloseBtn\');\n        let backdrop = null;\n        \n        // 手动显示模态窗口\n        function showModal(url) {\n            iframe.src = url;\n            backdrop = document.createElement(\'div\');\n            backdrop.className = \'modal-backdrop fade show\';\n            backdrop.style.opacity = \'0.85\';\n            document.body.appendChild(backdrop);\n            modalEl.style.display = \'block\';\n            modalEl.classList.add(\'show\');\n            modalEl.setAttribute(\'aria-hidden\', \'false\');\n            document.body.classList.add(\'modal-open\');\n        }\n        \n        // 手动隐藏模态窗口\n        function hideModal() {\n            modalEl.classList.remove(\'show\');\n            modalEl.style.display = \'none\';\n            modalEl.setAttribute(\'aria-hidden\', \'true\');\n            document.body.classList.remove(\'modal-open\');\n            if (backdrop) {\n                backdrop.remove();\n                backdrop = null;\n            }\n            iframe.src = \'about:blank\';\n        }\n        \n        // 关闭按钮\n        closeBtn.addEventListener(\'click\', hideModal);\n        // 点击遮罩关闭\n        modalEl.addEventListener(\'click\', function(e) {\n            if (e.target === modalEl) hideModal();\n        });\n        \n        btnOpenMap.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n            // 获取下拉框中选择的 A 端站点和 Z 端站点\n            const aSiteSelect = document.querySelector(\'select[name="interruption_location_a"]\');\n            const zSiteSelect = document.querySelector(\'select[name="interruption_location"]\');\n            \n            const aSiteId = aSiteSelect ? aSiteSelect.value : \'\';\n            let zSites = [];\n            \n            if (zSiteSelect && zSiteSelect.options) {\n                for (let i = 0; i < zSiteSelect.options.length; i++) {\n                    if (zSiteSelect.options[i].selected && zSiteSelect.options[i].value) {\n                        zSites.push(zSiteSelect.options[i].value);\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            \n            let url = \'/plugins/otnfaults/map/location/?picker=true\';\n            if (aSiteId) url += \'&a_site=\' + encodeURIComponent(aSiteId);\n            if (zSites.length > 0) url += \'&z_sites=\' + encodeURIComponent(zSites.join(\',\'));\n            \n            // 获取当前经纬度作为初始定位（如果有）\n            const currentLat = document.getElementById(\'id_cutover_latitude\').value;\n            const currentLng = document.getElementById(\'id_cutover_longitude\').value;\n            if (currentLat && currentLng) {\n                url += \'&q=\' + currentLat + \',\' + currentLng;\n            }\n            \n            showModal(url);\n        });\n        \n        // 监听来自 iframe 地图窗口的消息\n        window.addEventListener(\'message\', function(event) {\n            if (event.data && event.data.type === \'OTN_LOCATION_PICKED\') {\n                document.getElementById(\'id_cutover_latitude\').value = event.data.lat;\n                document.getElementById(\'id_cutover_longitude\').value = event.data.lng;\n                hideModal();\n            }\n            if (event.data && event.data.type === \'OTN_LOCATION_CANCEL\') {\n                hideModal();\n            }\n        });\n    }\n\n    // Z端快捷定位：根据A端站点自动查找有路径连通的站点，并提供快捷选择\n    function initPathShortcuts() {\n        const aSiteSelect = document.querySelector(\'select[name="interruption_location_a"]\');\n        const zSiteSelect = document.querySelector(\'select[name="interruption_location"]\');\n        \n        if (!aSiteSelect || !zSiteSelect) return;\n        \n        const aSiteTS = aSiteSelect.tomselect;\n        const zSiteTS = zSiteSelect.tomselect;\n        \n        if (!aSiteTS || !zSiteTS) {\n            setTimeout(initPathShortcuts, 100);\n            return;\n        }\n\n        // 创建快捷标签行容器\n        let shortcutsRow = document.getElementById(\'z-site-shortcuts-row\');\n        let shortcutsContainer = null;\n        if (!shortcutsRow) {\n            shortcutsRow = document.createElement(\'div\');\n            shortcutsRow.id = \'z-site-shortcuts-row\';\n            // 使用标准的 Bootstrap row 布局，并用 mb-3 保持与表单行距一致\n            shortcutsRow.className = \'row mb-3\';\n            \n            // 左侧留白 (匹配 label 的宽度)，右侧放置提示区域\n            shortcutsRow.innerHTML = `\n                <div class="col-sm-3"></div>\n                <div class="col-sm-9" id="z-site-shortcuts-container"></div>\n            `;\n            \n            // 将新行插入到 Z 端站点输入框这一行的正下方\n            let zRow = zSiteSelect.closest(\'.row\');\n            if (zRow && zRow.parentNode) {\n                zRow.parentNode.insertBefore(shortcutsRow, zRow.nextSibling);\n            } else {\n                zSiteSelect.parentNode.appendChild(shortcutsRow);\n            }\n        }\n        shortcutsContainer = document.getElementById(\'z-site-shortcuts-container\');\n\n        function fetchAndRenderShortcuts(siteAId) {\n            shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = \'\'; // 清空提示\n            if (!siteAId) return;\n\n            // 提示正在加载\n            shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = \'<span class="text-muted small"><i class="mdi mdi-loading mdi-spin"></i> 正在查找光缆路径连通站点...</span>\';\n\n            fetch(`/api/plugins/otnfaults/paths/?site=${siteAId}`, {\n                headers: {\n                    \'Accept\': \'application/json\',\n                    \'X-Requested-With\': \'XMLHttpRequest\'\n                },\n                credentials: \'same-origin\'\n            })\n            .then(res => res.json())\n            .then(data => {\n                if (!data.results || data.results.length === 0) {\n                    shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = \'<span class="text-muted small">该站点未查询到连通的光缆路径。您仍可自行搜索并选择Z端站点。</span>\';\n                    return;\n                }\n\n                // 提取连接的Z端站点并去重\n                const connectedSites = {};\n                data.results.forEach(path => {\n                    let connectedSite = null;\n                    if (path.site_a && path.site_a.id && path.site_a.id.toString() !== siteAId.toString()) {\n                        connectedSite = path.site_a;\n                    } else if (path.site_z && path.site_z.id && path.site_z.id.toString() !== siteAId.toString()) {\n                        connectedSite = path.site_z;\n                    }\n                    if (connectedSite && !connectedSites[connectedSite.id]) {\n                        connectedSites[connectedSite.id] = connectedSite;\n                    }\n                });\n\n                const siteIds = Object.keys(connectedSites);\n                if (siteIds.length === 0) {\n                    shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = \'<span class="text-muted small">该站点光缆路径可能为自环或无其他连接。您可自行搜索Z端站点。</span>\';\n                    return;\n                }\n\n                // 渲染快捷按钮\n                let html = \'<span class="text-muted small me-2">路径快捷选择：</span>\';\n                siteIds.forEach(id => {\n                    const site = connectedSites[id];\n                    html += `<span class="badge bg-info text-dark me-1 z-site-shortcut-btn" style="cursor:pointer;" data-id="${id}" data-name="${site.name}">${site.name} <i class="mdi mdi-plus"></i></span>`;\n                });\n                shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = html;\n\n                // 绑定点击事件\n                shortcutsContainer.querySelectorAll(\'.z-site-shortcut-btn\').forEach(btn => {\n                    btn.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n                        const idStr = this.getAttribute(\'data-id\');\n                        const nameStr = this.getAttribute(\'data-name\');\n                        // 尝试添加选中项到 TomSelect\n                        zSiteTS.addOption({\n                            value: idStr,\n                            id: idStr,\n                            text: nameStr,\n                            label: nameStr,\n                            name: nameStr,\n                            display: nameStr\n                        });\n                        // 注意：对于多选字段，addItem 默认是追加\n                        zSiteTS.addItem(idStr);\n                        // 可以选择性地给予一小点视觉反馈\n                        this.classList.replace(\'bg-info\', \'bg-success\');\n                        this.classList.replace(\'text-dark\', \'text-white\');\n                        setTimeout(() => {\n                            this.classList.replace(\'bg-success\', \'bg-info\');\n                            this.classList.replace(\'text-white\', \'text-dark\');\n                        }, 500);\n                    });\n                });\n            })\n            .catch(e => {\n                console.error(\'[PathShortcuts] 查找连接连通站点失败:\', e);\n                shortcutsContainer.innerHTML = \'\';\n            });\n        }\n\n        aSiteTS.on(\'change\', fetchAndRenderShortcuts);\n        \n        // 如果页面加载时 A 端已选中数值，仅渲染快捷选项不触发全局 change\n        if (aSiteSelect.value) {\n            fetchAndRenderShortcuts(aSiteSelect.value);\n        }\n    }\n\n    function initPlannedTimes() {\n        const displayEl = document.getElementById(\'display-planned-cutover-time\');\n        const historyContainer = document.getElementById(\'planned-times-history-container\');\n        const timesJsonInput = document.getElementById(\'id_planned_cutover_times\');\n        const mainTimeInput = document.getElementById(\'id_planned_cutover_time\');\n        const btnShowModal = document.getElementById(\'btn-show-planned-time-modal\');\n        const modalEl = document.getElementById(\'generatePlannedTimeModal\');\n        const backdropEl = document.getElementById(\'generatePlannedTimeBackdrop\');\n        const modalTimeInput = document.getElementById(\'id_planned_cutover_time_modal\');\n\n        if (!timesJsonInput || !historyContainer) return;\n\n        // 渲染历史记录\n        function renderHistory() {\n            let times = [];\n            try {\n                if (timesJsonInput.value && timesJsonInput.value !== \'null\' && timesJsonInput.value !== \'[]\') {\n                    let val = timesJsonInput.value.replace(/\'/g, \'"\');\n                    times = JSON.parse(val);\n                }\n            } catch (e) {\n                console.warn(\'解析计划割接时间记录失败:\', e);\n                times = [];\n            }\n\n            if (!Array.isArray(times)) {\n                times = [];\n            }\n\n            // 更新页面的“计划割接时间”只读文本展示及隐藏的主输入框以备表单提交\n            if (displayEl) {\n                if (times.length > 0) {\n                    displayEl.textContent = times[times.length - 1];\n                    if (mainTimeInput) {\n                        mainTimeInput.value = times[times.length - 1];\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    displayEl.textContent = \'—\';\n                    if (mainTimeInput) {\n                        mainTimeInput.value = \'\';\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n\n            // 动态更新按钮文本名称\n            if (btnShowModal) {\n                if (times.length > 0) {\n                    btnShowModal.innerHTML = \'<i class="mdi mdi-plus"></i> 设置一个新的割接时间\';\n                } else {\n                    btnShowModal.innerHTML = \'<i class="mdi mdi-plus"></i> 设置割接时间\';\n                }\n            }\n\n            historyContainer.innerHTML = \'\';\n            \n            if (times.length === 0) {\n                historyContainer.innerHTML = \'<span class="text-muted small ps-2">暂无历史时间记录</span>\';\n                return;\n            }\n\n            const listGrp = document.createElement(\'ul\');\n            listGrp.className = \'list-group mb-0\';\n            listGrp.style.maxWidth = \'500px\';\n            \n            const reversedTimes = [...times].reverse();\n\n            reversedTimes.forEach((timeStr, index) => {\n                const li = document.createElement(\'li\');\n                li.className = \'list-group-item cutover-time-record d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-1 px-2\';\n                li.style.fontSize = \'0.875rem\';\n                \n                let badgeClass = \'bg-secondary\';\n                let clockClass = \'text-muted\';\n                let textClass = \'\';\n                let latestBadge = \'\';\n\n                if (index === 0) {\n                    li.classList.add(\'is-latest\');\n                    badgeClass = \'bg-success\';\n                    clockClass = \'text-success\';\n                    textClass = \'fw-bold text-success\';\n                    latestBadge = \'<span class="badge bg-success text-white rounded-pill ms-2">最新</span>\';\n                }\n\n                const orderNum = times.length - index;\n                const orderText = `第${orderNum}次`;\n\n                li.innerHTML = `\n                    <span>\n                        <span class="badge ${badgeClass} text-white rounded-pill me-2" s